fields.name: ContentType
fields.description: The content type of the secret.

fields.name: SecretUri
fields.description: The URI to retrieve the current version of the secret.

fields.name: SecretUriWithVersion
fields.description: The URI to retrieve the specific version of the secret.

fields.name: Value
fields.description: The value of the secret. NOTE: 'value' will never be returned from the service, as APIs using this model are is intended for internal use in ARM deployments. Users should use the data-plane REST service for interaction with vault secrets.
